OL,3,CGirl, 5, dies and two people in
OL,4,Chospital after car crash
OL,6,FA young girl, 5, has died after a
OL,7,F"horrendous" crash involving two cars.
OL,9,FLancashire Police responded to the
OL,10,Fcrash involving a Skoda and VW Golf on
OL,11,Fthe A59 in Gisburn, Lancashire, on
OL,12,FThursday 21 May.
OL,14,FThe drivers of both vehicles and two
OL,15,Fpassengers, both aged five, were taken
OL,16,Fto hospital with serious injuries,
OL,18,FPolice have confirmed that one of the
OL,19,Fpassengers - a 5-year-old girl - died
OL,20,Fin hospital on Tuesday 26 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
