PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779905470
OL,3,CGirl, 5, dies and two people in
OL,4,Chospital after car crash
OL,6,FBoth of the drivers - a man in his 20s
OL,7,Fand a woman in her 60s - and the other
OL,8,Fpassenger remain in hospital.
OL,10,FPolice say the man who was driving the
OL,11,FVolkswagen Golf is being treated as a
OL,12,Fwitness in their investigation.
OL,14,FSergeant Laura Kendall from Lancashire
OL,15,FPolice said: "It is heartbreaking news
OL,16,Fthat the little girl has passed away
OL,17,Fand my thoughts first and foremost are
OL,18,Fwith her family and loved ones.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779905470
OL,3,CGirl, 5, dies and two people in
OL,4,Chospital after car crash
OL,6,F"My thoughts also continue to be with
OL,7,Fthe three people who remain in
OL,8,Fhospital being treated for the
OL,9,Finjuries they received in this
OL,10,Fterrible collision.
OL,12,F"I must stress that the investigation
OL,13,Finto the collision is ongoing, and it
OL,14,Fis still in its early stages in
OL,15,Fdetermining exactly what happened. We
OL,16,Fcontinue to appeal for anyone who
OL,17,Fwitnessed it or has dashcam footage
OL,18,Ffrom the area around the time it
OL,19,Fhappened ` who haven't yet contacted
OL,20,Fus ` to please get in touch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779905470
OL,3,CGirl, 5, dies and two people in
OL,4,Chospital after car crash
OL,6,F"If you have any information which you
OL,7,Fthink can help us, we want you to
OL,8,Fcontact us.
OL,10,F"We ask you to please refrain from
OL,11,Fspeculating about what happened. The
OL,12,Finvestigation will determine this and
OL,13,Fspeculative comments around what might
OL,14,Fhave happened can be very distressing
OL,15,Ffor the family of the little girl."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
